nl.tno.stormcv.util.connector

Class S3Connector

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tno.stormcv.util.connector.S3Connector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, FileConnector

    public class S3Connector
extends Object
implements FileConnector
    A FileConnector implementation used to access AWS S3 buckets. The S3_KEY and S3_SECRET to be used must be provided in the StormCVConfig. This connector is used for locations starting with s3://
    Author:
    Corne Versloot
